Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't all have magical horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've been meaning to move these older books to my reference section for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:22.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Got to keep the new books front and center!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:24.86,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.19,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,After all you have done for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.91,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,This is the least I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. I haven't done that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:33.53,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Nah. You just taught me the value of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.33,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Not much at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:37.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I may have offered some guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:40.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but you are responsible for the pony you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:42.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm proud to call you my student
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.47,0:00:45.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to get rid of theese boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike, can you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:47.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:49.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:52.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is it… a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.15,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Is it a parasprite?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:00:55.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's… It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:56.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,Incoming!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I usually get letters by dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:09.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,It is the fastest way to get mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:14.89,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.17,0:01:17.17,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Who'd be sending me a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:22.69,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,It's… the ponies from my old village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:23.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are they in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:25.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are they upset with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:26.30,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:27.44,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,It's worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.68,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,They've invited me to the annual Sunset Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.64,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Hey there, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:29.85,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,Hey, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:31.65,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:34.25,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I… I was invited…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:36.15,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,To the Sunset Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:40.32,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But we didn't think you'd actually show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.68,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,You didn't think we really wanted you here, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.37,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,But… I… apologised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.02,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I thought everything was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.81,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Please. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:01.00,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:07.96,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.77,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Is anypony there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:14.18,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.69,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.04,Luna,,0,0,0,,Dreams are my domain, Starlight Glimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.60,Luna,,0,0,0,,I am here because you need me to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.42,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,It's only a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.74,Luna,,0,0,0,,It may only be a dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.83,Luna,,0,0,0,,but the feelings in it are real.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.20,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:33.96,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,So I guess I'm more afraid of going back to the village than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.67,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:40.25,Luna,,0,0,0,,I have been helped time and time again by six very special ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.47,Luna,,0,0,0,,They helped me overcome my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.79,Luna,,0,0,0,,You're fortunate to have them as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.86,Luna,,0,0,0,,I suggest you share your concerns with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.97,Luna,,0,0,0,,I see much of myself in you, Starlight Glimmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.75,Luna,,0,0,0,,and I can tell you from personal experience
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.93,Luna,,0,0,0,,that things do indeed get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:10.90,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,…and Princess Luna said I should  tell you all how I was feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.08,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,So… There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.11,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to go back to the village for the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:18.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But why, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You went back to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.66,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Everypony has moved on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:25.22,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,But have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:27.57,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,They don't really know how much I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.22,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Or even worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.84,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,maybe I haven't changed as much as I think I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:33.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.72,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You are a totally different pony now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I mean, you were pretty awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.15,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:41.11,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What? She was!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.35,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:46.99,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think they would've sent the invitation if they didn't want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd be happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And getting an invitation to a party and not going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.57,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That's like…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:54.68,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's like…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:56.73,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know what it's like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.26,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,but it is definitely bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.54,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just be honest with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll understand where you comin' from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I understand how hard this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:08.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you took a friend along, it might make things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:11.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Somepony you trust who would look out for you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:19.39,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for doing this, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.88,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,When Twilight said I sould bring  a friend, you were the first pony I thought of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.94,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:28.30,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Asking me — Starlight's best friend —
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.70,Trixie,,0,0,0,,to help her on this difficult journey
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:33.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,really shows how wise a princess you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Trixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.43,0:05:38.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I was talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.74,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,The Festival lasts a whole week,  but I'm sure we won't stay that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.59,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know, Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:50.72,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Time really flies when you're spending it with your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:06:00.56,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Bye, Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:05.64,Trixie,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.92,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The town where you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.28,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,…magically stole everypony's cutie mark, replaced them with equal signs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.55,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,and forced them all to hide their natural talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.60,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:17.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I was going to say where you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.71,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But yours is a more…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,emotionally traumatic answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.49,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I just want to… blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.17,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Be just another pony in the crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.26,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,enjoying the Sunset Festival with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.66,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.26,Trixie,,0,0,0,,And if things get weird for you, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.44,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I've got your flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.76,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Is that a promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:36.98,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Not just a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:40.68,Trixie,,0,0,0,,A great and powerful promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.47,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't ask for more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.34,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,If we're gonna do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.43,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:01.18,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.32,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.82,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,We were worried you wouldn't be able to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.30,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,Are you staying the whole week?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.86,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,We have different events planned each day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.13,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,How is it living in the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.87,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,It is so good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:16.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.87,Trixie,,0,0,0,,These ponies are terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.21,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,It's good to see all of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:27.19,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,You got here just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.89,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,We were having some debate about these banners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.98,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,Which do you think feels more "sunsetty"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.71,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,You don't need me to decide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.06,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Whatever you think is probably best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.15,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.49,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,How about helping us with the routes for the relay races tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:44.74,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,Can you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.07,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I… I shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:48.39,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,You all go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.39,0:07:49.98,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I… I just want to enjoy the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:53.60,SomeponyLightPink,,0,0,0,,But you will be a judge for the baking competition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:57.48,DoubleDiamond,,0,0,0,,We had a few questions about the order  of the acts for the talent show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.97,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,And unicorns have a firework show planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.54,PartyFavor,,0,0,0,,We could really use your your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.93,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:21.10,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful Trixie would like to thank you all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.07,Trixie,,0,0,0,,for for being such an amazing audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.29,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Sadly, it is time for us to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.65,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Good night, fillies and gentlecolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.99,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I was horrible when I led that town!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.46,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I was ready for them to not trust me but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.63,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I wasn't ready for them to put me in charge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.03,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,With my past, I should never be in charge of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.18,Trixie,,0,0,0,,So you messed up. Big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:01.94,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Don't you ever tell another pony I said this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.24,Trixie,,0,0,0,,but even Trixie's made mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:05.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.88,Trixie,,0,0,0,,The trick is to just move on and pretend they never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.30,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I feel like that's almost good advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:21.34,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:24.50,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey… you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:28.47,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,So, you're probably wondering why I'm back so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:29.66,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:33.61,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I went to my old village… For the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun! How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.03,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,It was kind of a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.22,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I came back early because I freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.69,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Sounds awful! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:48.46,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,That was… strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Isn't she always strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.18,0:09:52.65,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.09,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.14,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.52,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Have you two noticed Pinkie acting a little strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.82,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie always acts strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:05.77,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.41,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I wanted to talk to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.41,0:10:12.58,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Things didn't go the way I thought they were going to go at the Sunset Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.69,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I kinda freaked out and ran out of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You freaked out and ran away from a festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:26.09,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,That's the funniest danged thing I've heard all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:30.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The decorations were terrifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,…Applejack for a friendship business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hello, ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.32,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We need Rarity and Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:46.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Very important friendship business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.41,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:56.31,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'm really not as impressed with your friends as the rest of Equestria is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.39,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.80,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:07.99,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:09.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:11.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight's very busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.59,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Spike, I really need to speak with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Make an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:17.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,She's a princess after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.21,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.38,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:22.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think a certain dragon didn't get his nap today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Right. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,He's been acting a little off all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think, he missed a meal or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.93,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,He's not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:37.51,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Everypony is acting a little strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:38.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's definitely been one of those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:43.92,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Not great actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.88,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,You are probably wondering why I'm back from the village so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to bring it up, but yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,it did seem strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Did it not go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:54.73,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,The town's ponies kept to asking me things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.75,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,like they expected me to be in charge again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.78,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,But being a leader is the last thing I should ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:01.33,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,So we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.55,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Very suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.51,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,In a literal puff of smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:05.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You should definitely never go back to that village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:09.88,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:13.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you were worried about what they thought of you before,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,it's probably way worse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'd cut my losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.36,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,That's… surprising advice coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:24.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm the Princess of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You don't need those ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:27.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can always make more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Speaking of friends, if you'll excuse me,  important business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.01,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,"Cut my losses"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:51.90,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:10.44,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Hey! I wanted to apologize for my behavior earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:14.68,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Party Favor. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I told you, you can never speak to them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.71,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Making sure you do what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm your teacher, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say to never come back here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.54,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Yes, but that just doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.65,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,You aren't acting like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.53,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.53,Luna,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.99,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,A dream? This is another dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.28,Luna,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.79,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.56,Luna,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.49,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.13,Luna,,0,0,0,,Starlight Glimmer, there's no time! You must get help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.11,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about? This is just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.12,Luna,,0,0,0,,Not here! In the waking world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.30,0:13:59.90,Luna,,0,0,0,,They taken my sister and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:01.54,Luna,,0,0,0,,It's worse than the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.06,Luna,,0,0,0,,Your dream called to me and I was able to break through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.39,Luna,,0,0,0,,You must find help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.45,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Who's taking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.55,Luna,,0,0,0,,Be careful who you trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.59,Luna,,0,0,0,,You need all the help you can find!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:13.38,Luna,,0,0,0,,The changelings have returned and…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.16,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:21.91,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:35.96,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.55,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie, it's Starlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.32,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.20,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Of course, Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:44.54,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'd love to perform for peanut butter crackers…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.97,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.67,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.04,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:02.82,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,It's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:05.22,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I think I figured out what's wrong with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:08.83,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I have a whole list of things that are wrong with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.01,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We can go read it in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.91,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,No, Trixie. We're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.73,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:21.32,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Aside from lack of sleep how are we in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.83,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I think, that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.47,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What did you tell me never to tell another pony?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Starlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.38,Trixie,,0,0,0,,If you woke me up to play guessing games…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.74,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,After we left my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.85,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What did you tell me to never
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.67,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,tell another pony, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:38.71,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That even Trixie makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.53,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie, there is no time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:43.76,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.55,Trixie,,0,0,0,,That even Trixie's made mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.17,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:48.29,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:49.80,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:50.80,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.60,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I just had to make sure, you weren't… one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.36,Trixie,,0,0,0,,One of who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:55.92,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,A changeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:59.21,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I think, they've taken Princess Celestia and Princess Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:15:59.68,Trixie,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:00.46,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.01,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I mean… What are we…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.56,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We have to tell Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.84,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,If I'm right, than it's too late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.06,0:16:37.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Just one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:47.90,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Queen Chrysalis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.21,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,I can't take any of you seriously when you look like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.37,0:16:54.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.08,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:04.23,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Now report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:07.23,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Everything here is going according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.95,Thorax,,0,0,0,,We've replaced the six ponies and their dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.26,Thorax,,0,0,0,,and have taken control of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.13,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.59,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,And I've just recieved word, that the princesses from Canterlot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.86,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,have successfully been replaced as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.74,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,We thought too small last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:28.75,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,One ponynapped princess wasn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:32.67,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,With all the most beloved ponies that Equestria taken care of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.12,Chrysalis,,0,0,0,,nopony can't stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.00,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I can't deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.15,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I'm just a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.69,Trixie,,0,0,0,,This is… this is princess-level stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.99,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But the changelings have all of the princesses…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:24.94,Trixie,,0,0,0,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:26.71,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:30.08,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Queen Chrysalis only said they took Luna and Celestia
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.91,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,and, obviously, Twilight and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:33.75,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,But maybe Cadence is still safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.33,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Our best bet is to get to the Crystal Empire before the changelings do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:37.95,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,That way we…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:40.34,Thorax,,0,0,0,,There's no help coming from the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.08,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Thorax?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:48.03,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.34,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Your wings look different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.47,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I guess they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.88,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,How do I know you aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.50,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,some other changeling pretending to be Thorax?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:05.66,Thorax,,0,0,0,,You were there when Spike defended me to the ponies of the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.57,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight said:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:09.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As the Princess of Friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I should set an example for all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:15.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But today it was Spike who taught me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.05,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay… I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.91,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,We don't need the whole speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:23.85,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Trixie, this is Thorax.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.66,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,He's a reformed changeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.86,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,He's on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:27.74,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:31.98,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Hi! It's a pleasure to…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:35.37,Trixie,,0,0,0,,If Starlight says you're on our side, I believe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.49,Trixie,,0,0,0,,But maybe just stay over there for now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.98,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,What did you mean there's no help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.06,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Did the changelings get Cadence too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:48.50,Thorax,,0,0,0,,They took Cadence, Shining Armor and Flurry Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.39,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Sunburst sent me here to get Princess Twilight's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:54.36,Thorax,,0,0,0,,But, but it sounds like it's too late for that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.45,Thorax,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.71,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Starlight, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.95,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,I… I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:04.75,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,There has to be somepony else who can handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.75,Trixie,,0,0,0,,There is nopony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:10.08,Trixie,,0,0,0,,Everypony with powerful magic is already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:12.75,Discord,,0,0,0,,You know, whenever ponies talk about powerful magic
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:14.15,Discord,,0,0,0,,they always leave me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:15.87,Discord,,0,0,0,,If I weren't so evolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:17.96,Discord,,0,0,0,,I might decide to take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:22.13,Discord,,0,0,0,,Well, isn't this quite a combination of secondary characters?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.64,Discord,,0,0,0,,Where're Twilight and the girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.25,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,First, how do we know that you are really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.46,Discord,,0,0,0,,Shall I continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.77,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Chrysalis and the changelings are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.77,0:20:43.04,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,They ponynapped all of the most powerful ponies in Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:47.47,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Celestia, Luna, Cadence, Shining  Armor, Flurry Heart, Twilight and her friends…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.25,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,We need to…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:50.34,Discord,,0,0,0,,They took Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:51.35,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.63,Discord,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.88,0:20:54.29,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,The changeling kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.97,Starlight Glimmer,,0,0,0,,With you on our side, I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:20:59.51,Discord,,0,0,0,,Odd…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.74,0:21:02.21,Discord,,0,0,0,,I was trying to take us right to Fluttershy, but
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.52,Discord,,0,0,0,,there is no Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:11.23,Trixie,,0,0,0,,I think I have a pretty good idea where she might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.35,Thorax,,0,0,0,,I've hoped to never see that place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:22.45,Thorax,,0,0,0,,Now what?
